    {
      "text": "A 36-week pregnant woman is diagnosed with preeclampsia and started on magnesium sulfate therapy. According to the Pritchard regimen, what is the total loading dose of magnesium sulfate administered initially?",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": 0,
          "text": "4 grams"
        },
        {
          "id": 1,
          "text": "10 grams"
        },
        {
          "id": 2,
          "text": "14 grams"
        },
        {
          "id": 3,
          "text": "5 grams"
        }
      ],
      "correct_choice_id": 2,
      "solution": "<p><strong>Correct Answer: C. 14 grams</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>Explanation:</strong></p>\n\n<p>Pritchard <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"988bd8e7c71692777197b9f1d5d5ca\">regimen</span> is a widely used protocol for <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"4d7ed0baae169277719199f6e9ab7b\">magnesium</span> <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"535af9a2181692777199309af44d24\">sulfate</span> administration in <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"a40b72bf2d1692777186cdae9f4e42\">eclampsia</span> <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"bc36e9b9381692777196b5f9a2f79c\">prophylaxis</span> or treatment.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Pritchard regimen: </strong></p>\n\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; width:0px\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Step</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Dose</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Route</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Timing</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Loading</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>4 g</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>IV</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Over 5 min</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Loading</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>10 g (5 g each buttock)</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>IM</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Immediately after IV</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Maintenance</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>5 g</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>IM</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Every 4 <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"136c4bdd441692777189c5b2e976a0\">hrs</span> in <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"d65e6c0e1616927771818ab537250d\">alternate</span> buttocks</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Duration</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>—</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>—</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>24 <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"136c4bdd441692777189c5b2e976a0\">hrs</span> post last seizure/delivery</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>Toxicity signs: Loss of patellar reflex, <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"cfad80a0f716927771979aae100f95\">respiratory</span> depression, <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"a37e635d211692777194eb7748e0cf\">oliguria</span> (<25 mL/hr).</li>\n\t<li>Antidote: 10 mL of 10% <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"54de8b79a91692777183e608bc0dd4\">calcium</span> <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"ff3235f97616927771884121a800e7\">gluconate</span> IV.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Preeclampsia</strong>: Pregnancy-specific <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"45372f6c361692777189ff3209e642\">hypertension</span> after 20 weeks with <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"1f58deccf71692777196e64781a01a\">proteinuria</span> or signs of organ dysfunction. Caused by <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"458e050fdc16927771809854c9fd53\">abnormal</span> <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"ecf18d570016927771959036300b40\">placentation</span> → endothelial dysfunction.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Eclampsia</strong>: <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"1fa06d396c1692777196050a5db718\">Preeclampsia</span> + new-onset generalized tonic–clonic seizures not attributable to other causes.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Use of MgSO₄</strong>:</p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li><strong>Seizure <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"bc36e9b9381692777196b5f9a2f79c\">prophylaxis</span> & treatment</strong> in severe <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"1fa06d396c1692777196050a5db718\">preeclampsia</span> and <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"a40b72bf2d1692777186cdae9f4e42\">eclampsia</span> (drug of choice).</li>\n\t<li><strong>Neuroprotection</strong> in imminent <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"ac9f7287191692777196e8c02d1f3d\">preterm</span> delivery (<32 weeks) to reduce risk of cerebral palsy.</li>\n\t<li><strong>Tocolysis</strong> (dose dependent- not used).</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Zuspan <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"988bd8e7c71692777197b9f1d5d5ca\">Regimen</span> (IV <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"988bd8e7c71692777197b9f1d5d5ca\">regimen</span> for eclampsia)</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li><strong>Loading dose:</strong> 4 g MgSO₄ IV given slowly over 5–10 minutes.</li>\n\t<li><strong>Maintenance dose:</strong> 1 g/hour IV <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"3562d699c516927771909a426ea8ef\">infusion</span> for 24 hours after last <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"5710e3461816927771987151d61aef\">seizure</span> or delivery.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>4 grams (Option A):</strong> Only represents the IV <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"00a5dcc74b16927771913b344e36a3\">loading</span> part, not the full initial <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"00a5dcc74b16927771913b344e36a3\">loading</span> dose.</p>\n\n<p><strong>5 grams (Option D):</strong> Incorrect as 5 g IM is the maintenance dose, not the <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"00a5dcc74b16927771913b344e36a3\">loading</span> dose.</p>",
